reviews.review_text:
Solid Show Out of the three aud show available, this one is the best sounding to my ears. And it's a groovy show to boot. Good, solid playing all the way through. I could really care less about "best ever this" or "best ever that." Blah, blah, blah. A good Dead gig is a good Dead gig. Period. This one's worth a download. Take it with you on a road trip. 
Peace and hang loose.

Great at times I was at this show. I remember I wasn't in a good space that night, so I can't say I can give an objective view of the show. I do remember the unbelievable "Music Never Stopped." It was so powerful at the end that it felt like the walls shook. That alone brightened my spirits; so much so, that I remember it to this day. Peace, and thanks for providing a portal to my memories.
